net.opentsdb.rollup

类 RollupQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.rollup.RollupQuery

  • public class RollupQuery
extends Object
    Holds information about a rollup interval and rollup aggregator. Every RollupQuery object will have a valid RollupInterval and Aggregator

        public RollupQuery(RollupInterval rollup_interval,
                   Aggregator rollup_agg,
                   long sample_interval_ms,
                   Aggregator group_by)
        Default constructor
        参数:
        rollup_interval - RollupInterval object
        rollup_agg - Aggregator object
        sample_interval_ms - Initial downsaple interval in milliseconds
        group_by - Group by aggregation.
        抛出:
        IllegalStateException - if rollup interval, rollup aggregator or group by aggregator is null

      • isValidQuery

        public static boolean isValidQuery(RollupQuery rollup_query)
        Does it contain a valid rollup interval, mainly says it is not the default rollup. Default rollup is of same resolution as raw data. So if true, which means the raw cell column qualifier is encoded with the aggregate function and the cell is not appended or compacted
        参数:
        rollup_query - related RollupQuery object, null if rollup is disabled
        返回:
        true if it is rollup query

        Tells whether the current rollup query sampling rate is lower than the initial request

      • getLastRollupTimestampSeconds

        public int getLastRollupTimestampSeconds()
        Looks at the SLA configured for the table to be queried and determines the timestamp of the latest data point that is guaranteed to be covered by the table.
        返回:
        last timestamp in seconds of the period guaranteed to be covered

      • isInBlackoutPeriod

        public boolean isInBlackoutPeriod(long timestampMillis)

        whether the timestamp is in the blackout period
